    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/12cd26d997ec066aff6b9b075bf07aac.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dragon's Brew is a board game cafe management sim! Serve customers while they play board games along with fufilling takeaway orders and delivery requests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/0004b531c53f7f2a045f82b8bb2eb7d1.poster.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/0004b531c53f7f2a045f82b8bb2eb7d1.webm?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/0004b531c53f7f2a045f82b8bb2eb7d1.mp4?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Bring your board game cafe to life in the vibrant seaside town of Pebblebrook. Source and grow your own ingredients, craft a variety of seasonal recipes, and expand your board game collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/180ec12d3e6c6838f0d45f9e9d7465f2.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=168 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Over 100 Food and Drink Items</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Bake, brew, and craft your own personalised menu with a wide variety of recipes. Unlock seasonal specials, explore dishes inspired by cuisines from around the world, and create your own signature dishes to serve and sell to your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/26a1f3bf54692383fd6a31a526dc8ea4.avif?t=1765453324\" width=800 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Build Your Board Game Collection</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Discover and unlock 100+ board games, each with its own effects and bonuses. Pair them with specific menu items to trigger unique effects and create powerful synergies that enhance your cafe’s operations and profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/578b748c136f68a068fbaad4ffca3ae0.avif?t=1765453324\" width=800 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Grow or Source Ingredients</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Cultivate and harvest crops from your own garden, or purchase everyday and rare ingredients from the local market, including special items sourced from beyond Pebblebrook to craft unique recipes for your cafe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/1127980a2dba08bdc149a4fd7fd809ec.poster.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/1127980a2dba08bdc149a4fd7fd809ec.webm?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/1127980a2dba08bdc149a4fd7fd809ec.mp4?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Customise your cafe</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Design and decorate your cafe to your taste! Create themed cafes inspired by board game genres, arrange furniture and props, and unlock new decor to make your cafe truly unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/dd27169aa69e90e7e8a7fc366256f25b.poster.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/dd27169aa69e90e7e8a7fc366256f25b.webm?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/dd27169aa69e90e7e8a7fc366256f25b.mp4?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Explore Pebblebrook and beyond...</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore the vibrant seaside town, meet quirky locals with unique stories and personalities, form friendships, and uncover the hidden secrets of Pebblebrook and beyond. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/6fd248806a79c1990f88b55e27d53619.poster.avif?t=1765453324\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/6fd248806a79c1990f88b55e27d53619.webm?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168560/extras/6fd248806a79c1990f88b55e27d53619.mp4?t=1765453324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Even More to Enjoy!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Run takeaway and delivery services, complete community quests, and engage in seasonal events that reward your progress. Discover hidden challenges, collect rare items, and experiment with different strategies to optimize your cafe and board game collection. Every choice affects the growth of your cafe and the happiness of your customers.</p>",
